                                    <div class="article-title">Artificial Intelligence-Based Clinical Decision Support Systems in Cardiovascular Diseases</div>
                                    <div class="article-authors">
                                                                                                                                    <a href="https://orcid.org/0000-0002-6582-3660" target="_blank">                                                      <u>   Serdar Bozyel</u> <sup>1</sup>
